# ReachBase

Get paid for your attention.

ReachBase is a decentralized paid messaging platform built on Base Network that allows creators, founders, developers, influencers, investors, recruiters, and professionals to monetize inbound messages.

Users set a custom USDC fee for receiving direct messages. Senders pay the fee on-chain, and creators earn revenue instantly. ReachBase combines Web3 identity, on-chain payments, creator monetization, and decentralized communication into a single platform.

